Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.35,0:00:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙海盗哥普拉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.41,0:01:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航向770.3
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.01,0:01:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要进入拉普鲁星的引力圈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.25,0:01:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉，你要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.93,0:01:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你照预定去拉普鲁星吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.89,0:01:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有很久没见吉古鲁老爹了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.75,0:01:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从海龟号完成后，有15年没见了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.33,0:01:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个顽固老头不知怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.77,0:02:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他虽然是宇宙第一的技师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.81,0:02:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却到处寻找金矿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在意的只有吉古鲁先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.33,0:02:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的孙女优子 今年应该是二十岁了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.93,0:02:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定了吧，哥普拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.09,0:02:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.53,0:02:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二十二话 地底之客
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.41,0:02:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个地方变得真多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊！越来越危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矿山都被挖空了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.01,0:02:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们渐渐搬离
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.45,0:02:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城镇开始萧条下来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上现在那帮人来了以后越发萧条了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么！这么窄还要我让路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔！你在这地方飞车当心坠入崖底
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.77,0:03:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.59,0:03:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在正在被基尔顿的机械艇追赶着！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.61,0:03:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔顿？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.01,0:03:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好惨！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个人，别让他逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.01,0:03:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:03:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上解决
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直开火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是打中了该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.93,0:04:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生紧急情况
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.29,0:05:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机械艇一艘在397坐标点被击毁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请马上支援
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.73,0:05:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人只有一人 可是拥有火力很强的枪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.77,0:05:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在由7点转往9座标点方向逃窜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经在雷达上发现他了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即派遣4艘前往第9座标点支援
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.33,0:05:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在会合前请待机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爹看到我一定会大吃一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.89,0:06:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱七八糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.69,0:06:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爹！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉古鲁老爹！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.73,0:06:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.77,0:06:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是哈里嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.81,0:06:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊，哥普拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.69,0:06:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥-普-拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.57,0:06:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人！长相不同！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来话长 我被基尔顿追杀所以只好改头换面啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你仔细看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.67,0:06:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是老样子，疑心病很重啊，哈里！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…整容技术第103型式的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在相信我了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.97,0:07:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，哈里，怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.21,0:07:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,录影带？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.49,0:07:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一年前录的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于来了，哥普拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看录影带的人八成是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会来这不毛之地找我的人也只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我快死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被他们弄成这个样子的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.53,0:07:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想保护矿山拼命战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.81,0:07:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是人已年老…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.81,0:07:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果更年轻一点的话\N就会像你一样 绝不会输给他们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.77,0:08:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两年前…基尔顿来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.01,0:08:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们把矿山的人接二连三地都赶出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.73,0:08:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔顿！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.61,0:08:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们可能在山里进行什么见不得人的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉，我要拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.09,0:08:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔顿不只抢了我的矿山
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还把我的孙女优子掳走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.89,0:08:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔顿的基地就在地下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.65,0:08:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我造了台钻地机，可以帮你到那里去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.33,0:08:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来是寻找矿脉的机器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,论性能比基尔顿的机型优秀很多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉，其它的哈里会告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了，哥普拉请把优子从基尔顿的手中解救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请去救优子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉，你要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里带我到钻地机那里去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:09:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉了他了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那男人看来已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.13,0:10:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么搞的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快追！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.05,0:11:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在砂中无法行动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那里玩砂到天黑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.05,0:11:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关闭钻石机
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.41,0:11:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸出辅助轮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.61,0:11:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.59,0:11:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.37,0:11:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钻地机就在那里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.01,0:12:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.03,0:12:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里快点把门打开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是群烦人的家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.13,0:12:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.03,0:12:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们就无法轻易进来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是吉古鲁老爹制造的钻地机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.21,0:12:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来这次的试机应该会很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那道门似乎是拉格合金制造的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.61,0:13:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.29,0:13:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收回辅助轮，开始用钻石机突击！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.01,0:13:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是客人们在门外等得不耐烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.61,0:13:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉！你知道怎么操纵吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.97,0:13:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.53,0:13:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会操纵的只有没装引擎的船
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.73,0:13:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就看你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.77,0:13:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！去，再加把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.21,0:13:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！冲进去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.37,0:14:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.57,0:14:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请求紧急支援
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.01,0:14:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请求紧急支援！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.21,0:14:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人得到强力的钻地机！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前向东南方123度方向逃亡中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.53,0:14:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近所有机械艇马上追击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.25,0:14:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5台啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.89,0:14:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舷70度确认敌人位置
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.97,0:14:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分成两队开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.77,0:15:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.21,0:15:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连游乐园的娃娃靶子都打不中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.01,0:15:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意前面！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.41,0:15:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的射距比我们更长！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.65,0:15:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再接近些攻击！遵命！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.85,0:15:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.81,0:15:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了！屁股被撵上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经到了他的后面了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.65,0:15:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们从左舷绕到他的前面去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.21,0:16:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！前面也出现了两艘啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.41,0:16:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他从正面冲了过来，而且速度很快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋，把他干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离 2000
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1500
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.97,0:16:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1000
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.01,0:16:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,800
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.77,0:16:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,600
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,500！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.45,0:16:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,22号机请回答！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,23号机到底发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让你活着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为你必须替我带路到基尔顿的基地去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.89,0:16:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉 船壳温度上升
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.47,0:16:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是钻的速度太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.91,0:17:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个洞到底连接哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.89,0:17:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些人到底是怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要靠过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子！优子！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.65,0:17:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了？哥普拉来救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子，你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.93,0:17:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子，你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.41,0:18:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉，这个洞穴很安全
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子，你…你还正常？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.09,0:18:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢下我一个人真是太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.97,0:18:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.61,0:18:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，优子，这里到底在做些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是基尔顿的地下毒品加工厂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.77,0:18:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挖采洛顿矿石经过提炼后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可做出比海洛英药性强20倍的毒品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.85,0:18:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他们绑架城镇的人\N都被强制注射了毒品来强迫他们劳动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不继续注射的话\N他们就会像刚才那些人一样，精神失常
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好毒的手段 真是太过分了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.01,0:18:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我装作吃过药后精神失常
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:19:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后混入了外面的人群才逃过一劫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.77,0:19:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.77,0:19:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下工厂的中心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.57,0:19:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.01,0:19:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们把洛顿矿石送到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.09,0:19:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再在这个塔内进行精炼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.45,0:19:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个庞大的工厂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.71,0:19:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排气口应该是通往地面的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.97,0:19:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们是能从哪里逃走了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.81,0:19:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先跑到那个塔再说了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.37,0:19:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现入侵者！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.65,0:19:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们正在向中心塔移动！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.01,0:19:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快阻止他们！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.21,0:19:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧我！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是发电室
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.53,0:20:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用这里的地热能源来发电
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.89,0:20:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.21,0:20:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要制造大型的烟火出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.77,0:20:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大事不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.89,0:20:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发电室的能量异常升高！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.09,0:20:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.37,0:20:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快启动紧急停止装置！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.69,0:20:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法启动！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.21,0:20:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要快点离开这里，这里就要爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所员搭乘机械艇脱离！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.21,0:21:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，我要借用一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.73,0:21:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，要出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那艘到底是想干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.05,0:21:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然倒退进入排气口！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.41,0:21:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉，我们掉下去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.79,0:21:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们掉下去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.49,0:21:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们掉下去了，哥普拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.81,0:21:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.85,0:21:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.05,0:21:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上升了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.49,0:21:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为能源炉爆炸了，有很多熔岩喷出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.81,0:21:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们要靠熔岩送我们到地面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.45,0:22:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太漂亮了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.73,0:22:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用来埋藏恶人…似乎太豪华了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.25,0:22:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.07,0:22:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样爷爷就瞑目了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.41,0:22:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和优子在熔岩上约会 真是太浪漫了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.79,0:22:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉，你真是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.81,0:22:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，哥普拉！住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.07,0:22:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要碰她！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.13,0:22:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么？这混蛋！可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.65,0:22:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机器人还会吃醋！怎么回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.09,0:22:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔的去休闲一下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.19,0:22:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且陪我的是像多明尼克这样的美女
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.96,0:22:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚想好不容易能享受一下就要受罪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.00,0:22:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就马上出大事件
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.13,0:22:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然想炸掉有5000人的客船
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.87,0:23:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还令我掉进海里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.37,0:23:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还被人下了毒药而失去知觉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.27,0:23:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.71,0:23:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集\N海底的墓标
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.41,0:23:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
